{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cd78eca6-2e7d-4c67-8f3d-0c1ad0b633e3","content":"Yes, you'll hit **framework compatibility issues**. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**MSTest v3 dropped support for older TFMs.** It requires:\n- **.NET 6.0+** (for modern .NET)\n- **.NET Framework 4.6.2+** (still supported)\n\nYour project targets three frameworks:\n\n| Target | MSTest v3 Compatible? |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Yes |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ No — EOL, not supported |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ No — EOL, not supported |\n\n**To migrate, you'd need to:**\n1. Update `net5.0` → `net6.0` (or later) and `netcoreapp3.1` → `net6.0` (or later).\n2. Replace the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages with the single **`MSTest`** meta-package (v3.x).\n\nWould you like me to perform the migration?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"5efcbfda-4a38-4bcf-ac90-f1755ffffa56","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user's project targets `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. They want to migrate from MSTest v2 (2.2.10) to MSTest v3. Let me think about compatibility issues:\n\n1. **MSTest v3 dropped support for older frameworks.** MSTest v3 requires at minimum:\n   - .NET 6.0 or later (for .NET Core/modern .NET)\n   - .NET Framework 4.6.2 or later\n\n   So `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` are problematic because:\n   - Both are out of support and MSTest v3 targets .NET 6+\n   - `net462` should work fine since MSTest v3 supports .NET Framework 4.6.2+\n\n2. **MSTest v3 consolidates its packages** into a single `MSTest` meta-package, replacing the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages. The migration path is straightforward—swap both out for one `<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.x.x\" />`.\n\n3. There are also API breaking changes in MSTest v3, including removal of deprecated APIs and modifications to assertions. The core compatibility blocker is the target frameworks—`net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` simply aren't supported by MSTest v3.","outputTokens":629,"requestId":"4C21:51CD1:2A9A0F:31ADA6:6A01423B"},"id":"fe8e6447-7a23-4e2f-989c-d6c15a399678","timestamp":"2026-05-11T02:43:20.457Z","parentId":"50ccce88-157c-4caa-af0e-273767aef63b"}
